OL,3,CRunner suffers broken arm and leg in
OL,4,Calleged motorbike hit and run
OL,6,FA runner suffered a broken arm and leg
OL,7,Fafter being involved in a suspected
OL,8,Fhit and run.
OL,10,FThe 56-year-old was out running with
OL,11,Fanother man on Derwent Walk, in the
OL,12,FLockhaugh Road area of Blaydon, when
OL,13,Fthey were allegedly approached by two
OL,14,Fmen on an orange motorcycle.
OL,16,FNorthumbria Police, which received the
OL,17,Freport just before 10.50am on Sunday
OL,18,F10 March, said the motorcycle is
OL,19,Freported to have hit the victim as
OL,20,Fthey were running.
